  "detailed_description": "Wakusei is a relaxing physics puzzle game about dropping and merging planets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/6fe114f8982a7d6f548b423e839f9624.poster.avif?t=1769089431\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/6fe114f8982a7d6f548b423e839f9624.webm?t=1769089431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/6fe114f8982a7d6f548b423e839f9624.mp4?t=1769089431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Drop planets around an eclipse to merge same planets into new ones. This might cause the extinction of some civilisations but it's okay, we asked them first.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/5fbdb84dcc3fb18ddb4b0882897db9f6.poster.avif?t=1769089431\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/5fbdb84dcc3fb18ddb4b0882897db9f6.webm?t=1769089431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/5fbdb84dcc3fb18ddb4b0882897db9f6.mp4?t=1769089431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The 360° gameplay makes for an interesting new experience and new strategies.<br><br>Compare your highscores to players worldwide.<br>Unlock upgrades, new events and additional game modes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/84898af290ec0f880db7bb1845648803.poster.avif?t=1769089431\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/84898af290ec0f880db7bb1845648803.webm?t=1769089431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/84898af290ec0f880db7bb1845648803.mp4?t=1769089431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Put the universe into a jar in Classic Mode or experience how the game must've felt like before gravity got invented in the Anti Gravity Mode.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/a2ce9fdada8f82d0485e6e51491fba3c.poster.avif?t=1769089431\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/a2ce9fdada8f82d0485e6e51491fba3c.webm?t=1769089431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2952140/extras/a2ce9fdada8f82d0485e6e51491fba3c.mp4?t=1769089431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
